c: 40
v: 28
t: "Gorko gom…óino…óo goo, jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen - suu…óunoo…óo gom…óinal mun - :\"E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: \"Joomi am ko Allah?\" Hara le o addanii on …ìanngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kanko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, he…ìay on\". Pellet, Allah fewnataa on fantinoowo fennoowo"